---
import Header from "../components/Header.astro";
---
<Header class="" style="font-family: Aboreto, serif;"/>
        <section class="mt-20 max-w-screen-xl mx-auto p-8 grid grid-cols-1 lg:grid-cols-2 gap-12">
            <!-- Left side -->
            <div class="space-y-12">
                <!-- Profile -->
                <div class="flex items-center space-x-6">
                    <div class="profilecircle w-32 h-32 rounded-full overflow-hidden">
                        <img src="img/4X9A8149 copy.JPG" loading="lazy" alt="profile image" class="w-full h-full object-cover">
                    </div>
                    <h2 class="text-2xl font-semibold">
                        Multimedia Designer<br><span class="text-lg text-gray-500">KEA Student</span>
                    </h2>
                </div>

                <!-- Contact Info -->
                <div class="space-y-6">
                    <h3 class="text-xl font-bold">CONTACT</h3>
                    <ul>
                        <li class="flex items-center space-x-3">
                            <span class="text-blue-500"><i class="fa fa-phone"></i></span>
                            <span>+45 29 62 48 32</span>
                        </li>
                        <li class="flex items-center space-x-3">
                            <span class="text-blue-500"><i class="fa fa-envelope-open-o"></i></span>
                            <span>c.koudal@gmail.com</span>
                        </li>
                    </ul>
                </div>

                <!-- Languages -->
                <div class="space-y-6">
                    <h3 class="text-xl font-bold">LANGUAGES</h3>
                    <ul>
                        <li class="flex items-center justify-between">
                            <span>Danish</span>
                            <span class="text-yellow-500"><i class="fa fa-star"></i><i class="fa fa-star"></i><i class="fa fa-star"></i><i class="fa fa-star"></i><i class="fa fa-star"></i></span>
                        </li>
                        <li class="flex items-center justify-between">
                            <span>English</span>
                            <span class="text-yellow-500"><i class="fa fa-star"></i><i class="fa fa-star"></i><i class="fa fa-star"></i><i class="fa fa-star"></i><i class="fa fa-star"></i></span>
                        </li>
                        <li class="flex items-center justify-between">
                            <span>Scandinavian</span>
                            <span class="text-yellow-500"><i class="fa fa-star"></i><i class="fa fa-star"></i><i class="fa fa-star"></i><i class="fa fa-star-o"></i><i class="fa fa-star-o"></i></span>
                        </li>
                    </ul>
                </div>

                <!-- IT Skills -->
                <div class="space-y-6">
                    <h3 class="text-xl font-bold">IT SKILLS</h3>
                    <ul>
                        <li class="flex items-center justify-between">
                            <span>Office Suite</span>
                            <span class="text-yellow-500"><i class="fa fa-star"></i><i class="fa fa-star"></i><i class="fa fa-star"></i><i class="fa fa-star"></i><i class="fa fa-star"></i></span>
                        </li>
                        <li class="flex items-center justify-between">
                            <span>Photoshop</span>
                            <span class="text-yellow-500"><i class="fa fa-star"></i><i class="fa fa-star"></i><i class="fa fa-star"></i><i class="fa fa-star-o"></i><i class="fa fa-star-o"></i></span>
                        </li>
                        <li class="flex items-center justify-between">
                            <span>Illustrator</span>
                            <span class="text-yellow-500"><i class="fa fa-star"></i><i class="fa fa-star"></i><i class="fa fa-star"></i><i class="fa fa-star-o"></i><i class="fa fa-star-o"></i></span>
                        </li>
                        <li class="flex items-center justify-between">
                            <span>Canva</span>
                            <span class="text-yellow-500"><i class="fa fa-star"></i><i class="fa fa-star"></i><i class="fa fa-star"></i><i class="fa fa-star"></i><i class="fa fa-star-o"></i></span>
                        </li>
                        <li class="flex items-center justify-between">
                            <span>HTML & CSS</span>
                            <span class="text-yellow-500"><i class="fa fa-star"></i><i class="fa fa-star-o"></i><i class="fa fa-star-o"></i><i class="fa fa-star-o"></i><i class="fa fa-star-o"></i></span>
                        </li>
                    </ul>
                </div>

                <!-- Personal -->
                <div class="space-y-6">
                    <h3 class="text-xl font-bold">PERSONAL</h3>
                    <p>I live with my husband and our two children. In my free time, I mainly spend time with my family and engage in smaller creative projects, as well as doing yoga and fitness at the gym when possible. I also enjoy good food, cultural experiences, and spending time with friends.</p>
                </div>
            </div>

            <!-- Right side -->
            <div class="space-y-12">
                <div class="about">
                    <h1 class="text-3xl font-bold">CHARLOTTE KOUDAL</h1>
                    <hr class="my-4">
                    <h2 class="text-xl font-semibold">Personal Profile</h2>
                    <p>I am naturally a very creative person with a sense of order. I love to “categorize” tasks, organize them, and approach them methodically. Once I get started, I am a hard worker with a lot of determination and follow projects through to completion. I am very service-oriented and enjoy building good relationships, whether face-to-face, over the phone, or digitally. I also have an easy time learning new IT systems. In addition, I speak fluent Danish and English and am used to working in both Microsoft and Mac environments. I am always seeking inspiration in the creative processes and constantly learning new tools and techniques.</p>
                </div>
            </div>
        </section>
 
